{"type":"text","timestamp":1781144976732,"sessionID":"ses_14b7dcdddffei484GOhlnbTHUq","part":{"id":"prt_eb48358a4001C4hMINBcl1c5cv","messageID":"msg_eb4833670001uTRkDnuBsPKhWz","sessionID":"ses_14b7dcdddffei484GOhlnbTHUq","type":"text","text":"The deep-review contract requires the lineage packet files plus per-iteration markdown and JSONL deltas. I’m now discovering the target spec contents and existing lineage state, read-only, before initializing any outputs.","time":{"start":1781144967332,"end":1781144976731},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c5b7db98421cf06016a2a1d8751d48191b5df6c7406cd8be5","phase":"commentary"}}}}
