D3 Traceability, spec/code alignment, checklist/task evidence, parent-child status consistency\n+- [ ] D4 Maintainability, doc drift, command ergonomics, future-safe automation surfaces\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## Non-Goals\n+- Do not implement fixes during review.\n+- Do not modify target files under review.\n+- Do not write outside this lineage artifact directory.\n+\n+## Stop Conditions\n+- Stop after convergence is legal across all configured dimensions, or after 6 iterations.\n+- Stop early only if all dimensions and required traceability protocols have coverage and the stabilization pass finds no new P0/P1 issues.\n+\n+## Completed Dimensions\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+| Dimension | Verdict | Iteration | Summary |\n+|-----------|---------|-----------|---------|\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## Running Findings\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+- **P0 (Critical):** 0 active\n+- **P1 (Major):** 0 active\n+- **P2 (Minor):** 0 active\n+- **Delta this iteration:** +0 P0, +0 P1, +0 P2\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## What Worked\n+- Initial scope discovery found a phase-parent packet with five completed child phases and no parent resource-map.\n+\n+## What Failed\n+- Code graph structural context was not trusted because the readiness marker reports stale graph state.\n+\n+## Exhausted Approaches\n+- None yet.\n+\n+## Ruled Out Directions\n+- Tool coverage expansion is out of scope; the packet explicitly scopes UX/docs/integration/automation around existing 37/8/9 tool coverage.\n+\n+## Next Focus\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+Iteration 1: correctness review of CLI shims and list-tools/completion behavior against child phase implementation summaries.\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## Known Context\n+- Parent packet describes five child sub-phases for daemon CLI front-door UX hardening.\n+- Child phase implementation summaries report completion for freshness/smoke, help/aliases/errors, reference docs, fallback envelope/bridge, and compact/completion automation.\n+- `resource-map.md` is not present at the parent artifact root. Skipping resource-map coverage gate.\n+\n+## Cross-Reference Status\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+| Protocol | Level | Status | Iteration | Notes |\n+|----------|-------|--------|-----------|-------|\n+| `spec_code` | core | pending | - | Compare parent/child requirements to CLI source/docs. |\n+| `checklist_evidence` | core | pending | - | Parent has no checklist by phase-parent design; child task lists provide completion evidence. |\n+| `skill_agent` | overlay | notApplicable | - | Target is a spec folder, not a skill. |\n+| `agent_cross_runtime` | overlay | notApplicable | - | Target is a spec folder, not an agent. |\n+| `feature_catalog_code` | overlay | pending | - | CLI feature claims need source/doc spot checks. |\n+| `playbook_capability` | overlay | pending | - | Smoke/help/completion playbook claims need spot checks. |\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## Files Under Review\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+| File | Dimensions Reviewed | Last Iteration | Findings | Status |\n+|------|---------------------|----------------|----------|--------|\n+| `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/spec.md` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `001-cli-freshness-and-smoke/*` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `002-cli-help-aliases-errors/*` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `003-cli-reference-and-skill-docs/*` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `004-cli-fallback-envelope-and-bridge/*` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `005-cli-automation-compact-completion/*` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `.opencode/bin/spec-memory.cjs` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `.opencode/bin/code-index.cjs` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| `.opencode/bin/skill-advisor.cjs` | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+| CLI source/hooks/docs named by child phases | - | - | 0 P0, 0 P1, 0 P2 | pending |\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n+\n+## Review Boundaries\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n+- Max iterations: 6\n+- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n+- Rolling STOP threshold: 0.08\n+- No-progress threshold: 0.05\n+- Coverage stabilization passes required: 1\n+- Session lineage: sessionId=fanout-gpt-1-1781144891515-7jxn7r, parentSessionId=null, generation=1, lineageMode=new\n+- Findings registry: `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n+- Release-readiness states: in-progress | converged | release-blocking\n+- Per-iteration budget: target 8-11 tool calls, max 12\n+- Severity threshold: P2\n+- Review target type: spec-folder\n+- Cross-reference checks: core=[spec_code, checklist_evidence], overlay=[feature_catalog_code, playbook_capability]\n+- Started: 2026-06-11T02:36:00Z\n+<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n","additions":102,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/review/lineages/gpt-1/deep-review-dashboard.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/review/lineages/gpt-1/deep-review-dashboard.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/review/lineages/gpt-1/deep-review-dashboard.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/review/lineages/gpt-1/deep-review-dashboard.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/016-cli-tooling-ux/review/lineages/gpt-1/deep-review-dashboard.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,28 @@\n+# Deep Review Dashboard\n+\n+## Status\n+- Provisional ver